  "title": "Hair Stylist",
  "description": "<p> We are expanding, and we’re looking for a <strong>passionate and skilled Hair Stylist</strong> to join our growing team</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />• Provide professional hair services (cut, colour, treatments & styling)<br />• Consult clients on suitable hairstyles and hair care<br />• Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of workstations<br />• Deliver excellent customer service and build long-term client relationships</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />• Minimum 1 years of relevant experience preferred<br />• Passionate about hair, beauty, and customer service<br />• Friendly, responsible, and a good team player<br />• Willing to learn and grow with the company</p><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br />• Attractive basic salary + commission<br />• Friendly and supportive work environment<br />• Opportunities for skills upgrading and career growth<br />• Staff benefits and incentives</p>",
